# undead
- dice: 3d6
  results:
    3: 1 spectre (night only)
    4: 1 banshee (night only)
    5: 1d6 wights (night only)
    6: 1d4 giant skeletons
    7: 1 ghast
    8: 1 large animal skeleton
    9: 1d6 zombies
    10: 1 small animal skeleton
    11: 2d4 skeletons
    12: 1 medium animal skeleton
    13: 1d6 ghouls
    14: 1d6 large skeletons
    15: 1 shadow (night only)
    16: 1d4 wraiths (night only)
    17: 1 ghost (night only)
    18: 1 vampire (night only)
